/Nh%E1%BB%AF-ph%E1%BA%A7n-3/poem-I-CHq9tXpmlwb63_Z6x4ow">Nhữ phần 3 - 汝墳 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bch/Th%C3%B9-du-ph%C3%A1n/poem-9NNArZ9kFVtGwc3bbCU_EA">Thù du phán - 茱萸沜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-%C4%90%E1%BB%8Bch/author-28bVUu4eMEqyWDansRayiw">Bùi Địch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Minh-Th%E1%BA%A7n/V%E1%BA%A1n-L%E1%BB%8Bch-ng%C5%A9-ni%C3%AAn-xu%C3%A2n-h%E1%BB%AFu-hi%E1%BA%BFn-ng%C5%A9-s%E1%BA%AFc-anh-v%C5%A9-gi%E1%BA%A3-chi%E1%BA%BFu-nh%E1%BA%ADp-chi-cung-ph%C3%BA-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-RS_jwXLHQDzMWUzVomaxzw">Vạn Lịch ngũ niên xuân hữu hiến ngũ sắc anh vũ giả chiếu nhập chi cung phú kỳ 2 - 萬歷五年春有獻五色鸚鵡者詔入之恭賦其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Minh-Th%E1%BA%A7n/author-YaMRkwvXgT5g5W4Ryp1GKA">Thẩm Minh Thần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-C%E1%BA%A3nh-Tu%C3%A2n/V%C3%B4-%C3%BD/poem-5OnWcaJLGsvxSrUG0ouJlg">Vô ý - 無意</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-C%E1%BA%A3nh-Tu%C3%A2n/author-iFMRIrLpJEb-YMTvWL1HJQ">Lê Cảnh Tuân</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
